tags.name: license-element
tags.description:
`license-element`
`A simple way of applying a semantically accurate license to work.`
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `license-element`
 * `A simple way of applying a semantically accurate license to work.`
 * @demo demo/index.html
 * @customElement license-element
 */

attributes.name: title
attributes.description: Title of the work.

attributes.name: creator
attributes.description: Person or group that owns / created the work.

attributes.name: source
attributes.description: Original Source of the work in question

attributes.name: license-name
attributes.description: License name, calculated or supplied by the end user if we don't have them.

attributes.name: license-link
attributes.description: License link for more details

attributes.name: license
attributes.description: License short hand. Options cc0,

attributes.name: more-link
attributes.description: More details link

attributes.name: has-more
attributes.description: See if we have more things to point to
